                    <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                        <ab>
                          <lb n="1"/><w lemma="καθοσιόω">καθωσ<supplied reason="lost">ιώθη</supplied></w> <rs type="institution" subtype="practice" role="decreeing" key="cheirotonia_meniaia" ref="#chersonesos"><w lemma="χειροτονία μηνιαῖα"><supplied reason="lost">χει</supplied><lb 
                        break="no" n="2"/>ροτονίᾳ μην<supplied reason="lost">ιαίᾳ</supplied></w></rs>.
                          <lb n="3"/><rs type="institution" subtype="board" role="incumbent" key="kosmos" ref="#chersonesos"><w lemma="κοσμέω">ἐκόσμιον</w> δὲ σὺν <persName type="attested" key="- f. Exakestidas"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                          <lb n="4"/>τῶ <name nymRef="Ἐξακεστίδας" type="patronymic">Ἐξακεστίδα</name></persName></rs> οἵδ<supplied reason="lost">ε·</supplied> <rs type="institution" subtype="board" role="incumbent" key="kosmos" ref="#chersonesos"><persName type="attested" key="- f. Timotheos"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                          <lb n="5"/><name nymRef="Τιμόθεος" type="patronymic">Τιμοθέω</name></persName></rs>, <rs type="institution" subtype="board" role="incumbent" key="kosmos" ref="#chersonesos"><persName type="attested" key="Alexas f. D-"><name nymRef="Ἀλεξᾶς">Ἀλεξᾶς</name> <name nymRef="Δ-" type="patronymic">Δ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></name></persName></rs>
                          <lb n="6"/><rs type="institution" subtype="board" role="incumbent" key="kosmos" ref="#chersonesos"><persName type="attested" key="Oikonomos f. Diosk-"><name nymRef="Οἰκονόμος">Οἰκονόμος</name> <name nymRef="Διοσκ-" type="patronymic">Διοσκ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></name></persName></rs>
                          <lb n="7"/><persName type="divine" key="Asklepios">Ἀσκλα<unclear>π</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ιῶι</supplied></persName>.
                          </ab>
                    </div>
                    <div type="commentary">
                        <p>La dedica ad Asclepio, di iniziativa pubblica, è stata promossa in occasione di una <foreign>cheirotonia meniaia</foreign>, espressione che sembra da intendere come riunione mensile dell’assemblea (<bibl><ref target="#bib1"><title>IC</title> I</ref>, p. 37</bibl>). La lista dei cosmi in carica alle linee 3-7, che menziona il cosmo eponimo all’interno dell’espressione ἐκόσμιον δὲ σὺν ... οἵδε, conserva in tutto quattro nomi di magistrati.</p>
                <p><emph>Elementi istituzionali o altri termini rilevanti</emph>: <ref type="inst" target="#cheirotonia"><foreign>cheirotonia meniaia</foreign></ref>, <ref type="inst" target="#kosmos"><foreign>kosmos</foreign></ref>.</p>
                    </div>
